data.description: This meticulously maintained 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath home, built in 2019, is situated in a well-established area that offers proximity to all amenities and doesn't have HOA. The open floor plan, lots of natural light , tile floors throughout and  plantation shutters, gives the house an inviting and distinctive ambiance.  The spacious kitchen boasts ample cabinet space, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. The oversized master suite includes a walk-in closet, a stunning shower, and double sinks. Large sliding doors lead to the back patio and large , fully fenced backyard, perfect for embracing the Florida lifestyle.  The property's strategic location places it just minutes away from downtown, Baldwin Park, Winter Park, a 30-minute drive from Orlando Airport, and a 45-minute commute to popular attractions like Disney World and other theme parks.
